### ShiftBookCategory Operations
##################################################

### Read All Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/ShiftBookCategory
Authorization: {{auth}}

###

### Read Category with Expand
GET {{baseUrl}}/ShiftBookCategory?$expand=mails,translations,workcenters,teamsChannel
Authorization: {{auth}}

###

### Read Single Category
### Replace CATEGORY_ID with actual UUID
GET {{baseUrl}}/ShiftBookCategory(ID=CATEGORY_ID,werks='1000')
