Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{auth}}

{
  "sendmail": 0,
  "sendworkcenters": 0
}

###

### Delete Category
### Replace CATEGORY_ID with actual UUID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/ShiftBookCategory(ID=CATEGORY_ID,werks='1000')
Authorization: {{auth}}

